.TH RND_IS_ABORT 3 DATE "librnd-VERSION"
.SH NAME
rnd_is_abort \- check if the library has been compiled with abort mode
.SH SYNOPSIS
.ad l
#include <rnd.h>
.sp
int
.BR rnd_is_abort (void)
.sp
Link with \fI-lrnd\fP.
.ad
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.BR rnd_is_abort ()
function can be used at runtime to determine whether the rnd library has been
compiled with abort mode or not.
.SH RETURN VALUE
The
.BR rnd_is_abort ()
function shall return 1 if abort mode is active and 0 otherwise.
.SH ERRORS
.P
The
.BR rnd_is_abort ()
function shall never fail.
.SH CONFORMING TO
See
.BR librnd (7).
.SH SEE ALSO
.ad l
.BR librnd (7)
